title: 2018 FIFA World Cup Russia ticket prices by category
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 7 different Ticket Types on X-axis for 4 groups Cat 1, Cat 2, Cat 3, and Cat 4. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Out of all 4 groups, Cat 1 had the highest SOME LABEL in Ticket Type Final (64) and Cat 4 had the lowest SOME LABEL in Ticket Type Group matches (2 to 48).
Among all the Ticket Types, Cat 4 had the highest SOME LABEL 110.0 in Ticket Type Final (64) and lowest value 20.0 in Ticket Type Group matches (2 to 48).
The maximum SOME LABEL for Cat 4 that was found in Ticket Type Final (64) was 5.5 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL observed in Ticket Type Group matches (2 to 48).
